{"tid":117563,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[髮型撚請入]方臉留緊長應該剪/電咩髮型好?","createTime":"2017-02-12T10:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T11:35:40.000Z","uid":78411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec0a902e66245846fbea63b88d344d700a4d53d6","tid":117563,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:15:58.000Z","msg":"我臉型似佢再方少少,都係唔立體,我隻耳比佢更貼耳<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.juqinglu.com/uploads/allimg/1411/1-1411022210144K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.juqinglu.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F1411%2F1-1411022210144K.jpg&h=cc3b9a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我之前諗住留林宥嘉而家既髮型,應該仲要留多兩三個月先同佢差唔多長<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgapi.nownews.com/?w=720&amp;q=60&amp;src=http://s.nownews.com/media_crop/153343/hash/a5/ac/a5ac0490487f176ea41b5d3a5d7cd571.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgapi.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D720%26q%3D60%26src%3Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fs.nownews.com%2Fmedia_crop%2F153343%2Fhash%2Fa5%2Fac%2Fa5ac0490487f176ea41b5d3a5d7cd571.jpg&h=47e1a86c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係留緊既同時發現如果兩邊愈大舊就愈顯得我面方<br />\n但係我又想留類似咁既style既頭<br />\n有冇髮型撚比下建議我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bee03763c8e071dc985912e7f02fa002e0a8bb","tid":117563,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:18:20.000Z","msg":"直接將張相上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔明你嘅形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3df16661ca81ecc9c805d2f173cd2140863539","tid":117563,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:19:26.000Z","msg":"方臉如果鏟光佢再留長鬚，型到爆炸"},{"pid":"c9dca45acbfeb2ffcef9bee2a1764911dac54e57","tid":117563,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:19:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接將張相上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm